Package: com.sinfool.disablefavoritesbuttonaction
Name: Disable Favorites "♡" Button/Action  ₃₋₁₉₋₁₅ ⚑
Author: Sinfool
Description: Disables the Favorites "♡" button/or just the action in the Photos app.  As a request via r/jailbreak, I added the ability to remove the "heart" icon which I've enabled by default.  Change the values if you'd just prefer the action disabled. Tested with an iP6+ 8.1.  (3-19-15) Disables the Favorites "♡" button/or just the action in the Photos app.  As a request via r/jailbreak, I added the ability to remove the "heart" icon which I've enabled by default.  Change the values if you'd just prefer the action disabled. Tested with an iP6+ 8.1.  (3-19-15)
